yuna: There's a rumor I heard when I was small.
yuna: A witch — who drove every monster back to this city alone. Singlehandedly ended the apocalypse.
yuna: Nobody knew her name. Nobody knew where she went after.
yuna: I used to think about that a lot.
yuna: What kind of person does something like that and then just disappears.
yuna: Baku has been in this city since she was — she didn't say exactly.
yuna: But the way she talks about it, the way she knows every corner of it...
yuna: ...the way she moves through it like it's an extension of herself —
yuna: It's a long story, she said. I'm probably wrong.
yuna: But I've been thinking about it since she said that. And I can't quite make myself stop
